long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This bookmark tool primarily implements a bookmark search function. As bookmarks accumulate over time, finding our previously saved bookmarks has become an inefficient task. With the search feature, we can now "instantly reach" any bookmark by simply entering keywords.
long.zh_CN: 该书签主要实现书签搜索功能。随着日积月累，找到我们以往收藏的书签已经是一件低效的事情，有了搜索功能，只要输入关键字，我们即可“秒达”。
